Campaign for @fwrd (LOVED my curls here & tempted to do another big chop)

One of the designers I’ve always loved because of their ability to connect fashion to the outdoor world so effortlessly was @ralphlauren. The classic silhouettes and quality designs that will stand the rest of time. That thought led me to wanting to go horseback riding! Coming from Kenya, I’ve always loved animals and they gentle nature. Shamrock was such a good boy and Calabasas was beautiful 🐎☀️

While staying in Paris, I had an amazing time with Ralph Lauren at The Garden at Ralph’s Restaurant. The beautiful garden outside, the decor inside, and of course the food. The Caesar salad was the best salad so fresh and crisp. Don’t get me started on the salmon! It was perfect, and couldn’t had asked for a better lunch. Thank you the whole team and management for such an amazing lunch 🫶🏽
Habibi @ralphlauren  شكرًا لك for an amazing meal and time until next time Paris 🫶🏾
